+COMMAND workspace-init
+SYNOPSIS: python3 scripts/cypilot.py workspace-init [--root <path>] [--output <path>] [--inline] [--force] [--max-depth <N>] [--dry-run]
+DESCRIPTION: Initialize a multi-repo workspace by scanning nested sub-directories for repos with cypilot directories (.git or AGENTS.md marker). Generates a standalone .cypilot-workspace.toml or inline [workspace] section in config/core.toml. Creates an empty workspace when no nested repos are found, allowing incremental source addition via workspace-add.
