+### Workspace Sync
+
+- [x] `p1` - **ID**: `cpt-cypilot-flow-workspace-sync`
+
+**Actors**:
+
+- `cpt-cypilot-actor-user`
+- `cpt-cypilot-actor-cypilot-cli`
+
+**Success Scenarios**:
+- User runs `workspace-sync` → all Git URL sources fetched and worktrees updated to match remote
